MBOMBELA &#8211; The City of Mbombela Local Municipality has set up a road block towards White River.Municipality spokesman Mr Joseph Ngala said the aim of the operation was to recoup outstanding traffic fines from motorists.&#8220;We will be conducting road blocks unannounced throughout the municipality in our efforts to get what is rightfully ours,&#8221; he said.It is not clear when regular flow will be restored.